rows.label: qst100410_msg0101
rows.name:
Meehhh! Solala was only
swimming in Cloud Sea!

rows.label: qst100410_msg0102
rows.name: No! No! Won't go with you!

rows.label: qst100410_msg0201
rows.name:
Falala is very sad because
her son went missing. Will
you at least meet with her?

rows.label: qst100410_msg0202
rows.name:
At worst you'll get to enjoy
that famous food and singing
you heard all about!

rows.label: qst100410_msg0203
rows.name:
Falala misses her son so much.
She'd probably be happy just to
see someone who looks like him.

rows.label: qst100410_msg0204
rows.name:
At least come and try some of that
famous grub and hear her sing?

rows.label: qst100410_msg0205
rows.name:
Hey, Falala is super sad since her
son went missing. Come see her -
what's the worst that could happen?

rows.label: qst100410_msg0206
rows.name:
At the very least you'll get
to have some of that famous
food and hear her sing.

rows.label: qst100410_msg0207
rows.name:
Falala very sad since sonnypon
go missing. Maybe Solala could
meet her, just little bit?

rows.label: qst100410_msg0208
rows.name:
Listen to song, eat delicious
food... Make Falala happy again!

rows.label: qst100410_msg0209
rows.name:
Hmm, I had no idea that Invidian Nopon
were so heartless. Falala is in great
distress over her missing son.

rows.label: qst100410_msg0210
rows.name:
A true Invidian would sit with her,
enjoy her food and song, and provide
her a little solace from her misery.

rows.label: qst100410_msg0211
rows.name:
Oh all right then! Solala do
it! Solala is red-blooded
Nopon of Invidia Kingdom!

rows.label: qst100410_msg0212
rows.name:
Solala will meet and explain
that he not sonnypon of Falala.

rows.label: qst100410_msg0213
rows.name: Maybe even try to comfort a little!

rows.label: qst100410_msg0214
rows.name:
But only going because of
famous food and singing really!
Other stuff just extra!
